ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations (Czech Republic)
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS (visa requirement Czech Republic), which will remove Czech Republic from the list of countries and territories whose citizens are exempt from the temporary resident visa requirement for travel to Canada under subsection 190(1) of the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations.
